{
  "name": "Branding Smite",
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As you hit with a weapon attack or unarmed strike, your strike gleams with astral radiance, and the attack deals an extra 2d8 plus your spellcasting ability modifier radiant damage to the target. Additionally, the target becomes visible if it is invisible, and the target sheds dim light in a 5-foot radius and cannot become invisible until the end of your next turn or until the spell ends if you choose to maintain concentration on this spell.</p><p></p><p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the extra damage increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 2nd.</p>",
